	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=300874"><span id=" ">GobgobfrumGrobb</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">8 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>I make these on Maelin Starpyre server (am a GM troll blacksmith).<br/>I don't think I've come across another GM Troll Blacksmith.<br/><br/>At 252 skill (max skill with mod item) I'm lucky to have a 50% success rate on these.<br/>I found attempting them at less than GM smith skill was a waste of time as the success rate falls off sharply at lower proficiency.<br/><br/>I don't advertise these on my server because I figure there is better out there with PoP and LDoN nowdays but despite that the last 10 or so I've sold in the last 6months were from ppl tracking me down and asking for them to be made - both the 12/21 deity and 12/22 normal versions.<br/><br/>Feedback I've had was that they proc' nicely and maintain aggro very well on account of the proc'.<br/>As one of the earlier posts hypothosised - they do seem to be predominantly requested by lvl 45-55 non-uber-guilded ppl.<br/><br/><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Feb&nbsp;&nbsp;2 12:58:14 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Good bashin' too yoo<br/>Gobgob frum Grobb</td></tr>
